### Our Strategic Approach

**Differentiation:** Rather than organising by season like every competitor, we organise by color family with the "why" built in — color wheel logic, hair shade nuance, and skin undertone context. We are the first resource to address strawberry blonde vs. copper vs. auburn as distinct audiences. We answer the questions the community actually debates (can redheads wear orange? red? neon?) with real nuance rather than vague warnings.

